===Hardware specification=== *CPU: ''[[Allwinner]]'' H2+ @1.2GHz Quad-core ARM (Cortex-A7) <!-- H.265/HEVC 4K --> *GPU: ''Mali-400MP2'' @600MHz (supports OpenGL ES 2.0) *Memory: 256MB/512MB (DDR3) SDRAM (shared with GPU) *Onboard Storage: TF card (max. 32GB)/MMC card slot :16MB (SPI NOR) Flash (not soldered on the first batch) *2x USB 2.0, CIR receiver, microphone and combined AV/TRRS jack :are available via 13-pin header (supported by [https://www.aliexpress.com/store/product/New-Orange-Pi-Zreo-Expansion-board-Interface-board-Development-board-beyond-Raspberry-Pi/1553371_32770665186.html?isOrigTitle=true Expansion board])
